  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TPa27">
<l>kūṭārai vellum cīr kōvintā vuntaṉṉaip</l>
<l>pāṭip paṟai koṇṭu yām peṟum cammāṉam</l>
<l>nāṭu pukaḻum pariciṉāl naṉṟākac</l>
<l>cūṭakamē tōḷ vaḷaiyē tōṭē cevip pūvē</l>
<l>pāṭakamē yeṉṟaṉaiya palkalaṉum yām aṇivōm</l>
<l>āṭai yuṭuppōm ataṉ piṉṉē pāṟ cōṟu</l>
<l>mūṭa ney peytu muḻaṅkai vaḻi vārak</l>
<l>kūṭi yiruntu kuḷirntēlōr empāvāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O excellent Govinda who win over the foes!</l>
<l>The rewards that</l>
<l>we [are to] get having sung about You [and]</l>
<l>acquired the paṟai-drums [are]:</l>
<l rend="indent">bracelets, upper-arm rings, ola rolls, ear-jewels, anklets, and so forth</l>
<l rend="indent">of a quality praised by world.</l>
<l>We shall wear nicely many such jewels; we shall wear garments.</l>
<l>After that, we shall stay together and be satisfied,</l>
<l rend="indent">pouring ghee such that it covers the milk-rice,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] trickles down [our] elbows!</l>
<l>O our maidens, accept [and] consider [this] attentively!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
